songs.title: Shooting
songs.lyrics:
I'm going to count only 10
It's the moment I give you

I'm waiting
I'm waiting

I want you to do it
Let's do it

SHOOT!!!!

The dust is blown from here
Do not even look at me, I assure you

Ah? Que?

I will give you up to 5
I want you to do it but now

I want you to shoot, I ask you

I finally had the strength to do it
But I want you to personally do it

SHOOT!!!!

The dust is blown from here

I will give you up to 5
I want you to do it but now

Shoot, shoot, shoot at me
Do it, here and now
I will not wait any longer, give me the weapon !!!!!
